PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Garbage Trading App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the garbage trading app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects waste producers with recyclers and buyers, allowing them to trade recyclable materials efficiently. Users can list their waste, browse available materials, and arrange transactions all within the platform.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What types of waste can be traded on the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: The app supports trading of various recyclable materials including plastics, metals, paper, electronics, and organic waste. Users can specify the type and quantity of waste they're offering or seeking.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Currently, our app is available in select regions, with plans for global expansion. Check our website for the most up-to-date list of supported countries and cities.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How do you ensure the quality of traded materials?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We implement a user rating system and encourage detailed descriptions and photos of materials. Additionally, we provide guidelines for proper waste sorting and quality assessment to maintain high standards in our trading community.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our garbage trading app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is the garbage trading app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our garbage trading app is a platform that connects waste generators with recyclers and waste management companies, allowing users to buy, sell, and trade various types of recyclable materials and waste products.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Users can list their recyclable materials or waste for sale, browse available listings, and connect with potential buyers or sellers. The app facilitates secure transactions and provides tracking for waste collection and delivery.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What types of waste can be traded on the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our app supports trading of various recyclable materials such as paper, plastic, metal, glass, and electronic waste. Users can also trade organic waste for composting and other specialized waste streams.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app available in my area?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We are continuously expanding our service areas. Please check the app or our website for the most up-to-date information on supported locations. If we're not in your area yet, you can join our waitlist for future updates.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How does the app ensure compliance with waste management regulations?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our app incorporates local and national waste management regulations into its framework. We verify users' credentials and certifications, and provide guidance on proper handling and transportation of waste materials to ensure compliance with all applicable laws and regulations.
